description:
This is part 1/5 of an evolutionary steering behaviors coding challenge. The goal is to create a system where autonomous steering agents evolve the behavior of eating food (green dots) and avoiding poison (red dots).This challenge is part of the spring 2017 ITP "Intelligence and Learning" course.

💻Challenge: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/069.1-steering-evolution.html
